    <item>
      <title>京东方的哈斯克尔表示，英国在人工智能竞赛中落后于美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-is-falling-behind-us-in-the-race-for-ai-boe-s-haskel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行政策制定者乔纳森·哈斯克尔表示，美国在人工智能投资方面领先于英国，引发了人们对生产率差距扩大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-is-falling-behind-us-in-the-race-for-ai-boe-s-haskel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚将造成电信损失数十亿美元的光缆损坏定为刑事犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/nigeria-to-criminalise-fiber-cable-damage-costing-telecoms-billions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在 MTN 尼日利亚通信公司和其他电信公司多次抱怨他们损失了数十亿奈拉之后，尼日利亚将把破坏宽带光缆定为刑事犯罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/nigeria-to-criminalise-fiber-cable-damage-costing-telecoms-billions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:45:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国 LG 发行美元债券为 ESG 项目融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/electronics-giant-lg-debuts-dollar-bond-to-finance-esg-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG电子公司正在出售以美元计价的债券，以部分帮助这家韩国家电制造商为可持续发展计划提供资金，这是该公司首次发行此类债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/electronics-giant-lg-debuts-dollar-bond-to-finance-esg-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:00:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚向外国人开放珍贵咖啡出口大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/ethiopia-opens-door-for-prized-coffee-exports-to-foreigners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大的咖啡生产商修改了规则，允许外国公司直接从农民和加工商那里购买商品，这是东非最大经济体自由化的最新改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/ethiopia-opens-door-for-prized-coffee-exports-to-foreigners</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:05:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国海军尝试实验技术来帮助保护关岛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/us-navy-trying-experimental-tech-to-protect-guam-from-hacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国海军已转向实验性技术来保护远程但关键的网络免受中国黑客的攻击，并与一家小型移动运营商签署了一份合同，为关岛的电信公司提供网络安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/us-navy-trying-experimental-tech-to-protect-guam-from-hacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 从 eBay 的最大熊市转变为人工智能领域的最大牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/morgan-stanley-flips-from-ebay-s-biggest-bear-to-top-bull-on-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[eBay Inc. 对人工智能的拥抱让对该股最悲观的分析师变成了其最大的粉丝，摩根士丹利预计该股明年将进一步上涨 25%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/morgan-stanley-flips-from-ebay-s-biggest-bear-to-top-bull-on-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于客户保持谨慎态度，印孚瑟斯销售预测低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/infosys-sales-forecast-falls-short-as-clients-hold-off-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Infosys Ltd.预计今年的销售增长将不温不火，这表明海外客户正在限制科技支出，直到全球经济加速增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/infosys-sales-forecast-falls-short-as-clients-hold-off-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于消费疲软持续，台积电下调芯片市场前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/tsmc-posts-first-profit-growth-in-a-year-after-global-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台积电下调了芯片市场扩张的预期，警告称智能手机和个人电脑市场依然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/tsmc-posts-first-profit-growth-in-a-year-after-global-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
