    <item>
      <title>美光科技将于下周宣布获得超过 60 亿美元的芯片补助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/micron-mu-to-get-over-6-billion-in-chips-act-grants-in-announcement-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机内存芯片制造商美光科技公司 (Micron Technology Inc.) 准备从商务部获得 61 亿美元的拨款，以帮助支付国内工厂项目的费用，这是将半导体生产带回美国本土的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/micron-mu-to-get-over-6-billion-in-chips-act-grants-in-announcement-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 23:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
